{"tid":258932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"討論下大家點睇虐待動物即標準","createTime":"2017-05-26T13:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T06:45:43.000Z","uid":52210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9964175b87c89fd3ffd71961a6db1c0fbc105783","tid":258932,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"事緣小弟碌fb睇到fd share左個廣告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1545972845647417/videos/1926587504252614/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1545972845647417%2Fvideos%2F1926587504252614%2F&d=EkSOzQ7ZVjnG5t8dBASUijOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=be25766a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1545972845647417/videos/1926587504252614/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完覺得idea幾好幾抵死<br />\n甚至令我覺得其實女人都幾辛苦<br />\n<br />\n可惜既係我一碌落去睇到d cm<br />\n大部分都係屌緊個廣告虐待動物<br />\n小弟睇翻<br />\n發覺除左b cup (豚鼠)之外<br />\n大部分都唔係郁得好犀利<br />\n睇得出個演員都就住就住<br />\n但其實豚鼠個個都唔算郁得好犀利<br />\n<br />\n小弟覺得虐待動物個標準係咪已經降到咁低<br />\n我一直以為虐待動物係個d<br />\n變態主人，唔人道馬戲團同動物商人<br />\n但原來宜家搵隻動物翻黎拍片都算係虐待<br />\n<br />\n講翻個廣告<br />\n好多人屌寵物類型既動物比人虐待<br />\n雞反而就冇人講<br />\n咁雞算唔算係動物？<br />\n雞比你地無視算唔算係虐待動物？<br />\n定係你地班主人已經覺得寵物同動物係兩回事？<br />\n<br />\n利申 小弟絕對唔支持虐待動物<br />\n只係想探討下點先為之虐待動物"},{"pid":"69294dcd135dceef2f442f85cb85cb76062c19c8","tid":258932,"uid":118314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:25:08.000Z","msg":"好簡單，隻動物可愛就係虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed6f3085fa6a297df24455cbea292ca31bf4137","tid":258932,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/142604_5b1f46951d5bde2ddf72a9ab171f246c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F142604_5b1f46951d5bde2ddf72a9ab171f246c.jpg&h=07aafbb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07676fc1329b91d01afba521a3c2f3b71d41c3ef","tid":258932,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"睇黎d cm都係一面倒覺得係虐待"},{"pid":"63f95c78e203c036bb1f44b180c4666fc11bf895","tid":258932,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎d cm都係一面倒覺得係虐待</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n總之佢地「覺得」「望落」「好似」好慘，就會覺得係虐待，同埋只限於哺乳類、鳥類同部份爬蟲類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}